snippet.title: Orbiz Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming Soon on Steam http://store.steampowered.com/app/572480/

Orbiz is a top-down game with rogue-like elements, designed for both singleplayer and local multiplayer. The primary objective of the game is to engage in three levels of combat with various zombies on each spherical world before locating the portal to travel to the next one.
